replies.body:
This reply alone deserves commemoration. I do believe the majority of the people complaining aren't able to be objective of their own play.{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
I'm sitting @ Plat 2 right now and the only thing I can think of is how hard it is to deal with warmogs {{champion:31}}  having 13k hp lol. Maybe at the most {{champion:142}}  needs some attention and have more of her power shifted to her auto attack, seeing as she hardly ever needs it on a squishy. But even then if you don't have an ally to block for you or one with a brain to space his body block so the aoe doesn't inadvertently tag you anyway, you should be dead.{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}} 
{{champion:119}}  Might need some attention but for other reasons. Sometimes you shouldn't pick that {{champion:11}} or {{champion:121}} when your team is lacking cc that would otherwise keep your team competitive.
